---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

export const title = 'About AdlerPrice';
---

<BaseLayout title={title}>

<section class="py-12 px-6">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-playfair mb-6">About AdlerPrice</h1>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    Since 1988, AdlerPrice has been at the forefront of architectural consulting, specializing in Architect Negligence Claims, Consulting, and Design Thinking. Our practice has undertaken a wide range of work, from incisive interventions using modest materials to large-scale strategic planning and multi-storey developments.
  </p>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    We pride ourselves on our strong design, documentation, and project administration skills. Our early experience in luxury homes has equipped us with extensive expertise across projects of varied scale and complexity.
  </p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-playfair mt-8 mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    At AdlerPrice, we believe in a collaborative approach to design and consulting. Our philosophy centers around understanding our clients' needs and delivering tailored solutions that reflect their vision while adhering to the highest standards of quality and professionalism.
  </p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-playfair mt-8 mb-4">Expertise</h2>
  <p class="text-lg mb-4">
    Our expertise spans various sectors, allowing us to tackle complex challenges with innovative solutions. We are committed to continuous learning and adapting to the evolving landscape of architecture and design.
  </p>
</section>

</BaseLayout>